--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Lucide  (https://lucide.dev)

Some icons in this package are derived from, or modified from, Lucide, an
open-source icon library. Where icons originate from Lucide — whether shipped
as-is or after modification — the ISC license terms reproduced below apply to
those source materials. Modifications made by Acronis are released under the
MIT license stated above. The package does not currently track per-asset
provenance; if you need to identify which specific icons derive from Lucide,
open an issue.

